Compiling releases:

Suggestion:
Install gvm for managing go installations
https://github.com/moovweb/gvm

Requirements:
Install gox (go cross compiler):
https://github.com/mitchellh/gox

Install golang-nw-pkg:
go get github.com/lonnc/golang-nw/cmd/golang-nw-pkg


Building skycoin releases:
./build-$OS-$ARCH.sh

All scripts must be run from this directory

Core configurations per OS/ARCH are in $OS-$ARCH-config.  Don't edit these.

Compressed releases are put in ./releases/
